## CLASS DESIGN RULES

### Required Fields
```csv
name,hit_die,primary_stat,saves,features
```

### Hit Die by Role
| Role | Hit Die | Primary Stat |
|------|---------|--------------|
| Tank/Frontline | d10-d12 | STR or CON |
| Striker/DPS | d8 | DEX or CHA |
| Controller/Support | d6-d8 | INT or WIS |
| Face/Social | d8 | CHA |

### Feature Naming Convention
All class features should be re-flavored from classic TTRPG abilities with digital nomad theming:
- `Original Ability (Themed Name)`
- Example: `Action Surge (Hustle)`, `Sneak Attack (Hidden Fees)`, `Divine Smite (Code Review)`

### Saves Format
```
[Primary Stat]/[Secondary Stat]
Examples: Cha/Dex, Int/Wis, Str/Con
```

