## SKILL DESIGN RULES

### Required Fields
```csv
name,ability,description,example_use
```

### Skill-to-Stat Mapping
Every skill MUST be tied to exactly ONE ability:

| Ability | Skills |
|---------|--------|
| **STR** | Gentrification, forcing physical compliance, intimidation through presence |
| **DEX** | Ghosting, Latte Art, Touch Typing, Selfie Taking, Parallel Parking, evasive maneuvers |
| **CON** | Doomscrolling, Power Napping, endurance-based tasks, meeting survival |
| **INT** | Cryptocurrency Lore, Subletting, Tech Troubleshooting, IKEA Assembly, algorithm analysis |
| **WIS** | WiFi Dowsing, Trend Analysis, Manifesting, Vibe Checking, intuition-based perception |
| **CHA** | Content Creation, Slack Etiquette, Humblebragging, Therapy Speak, social manipulation |

### Special Skills
- **Persuasion** → Subset of CHA (Barista Negotiation, Mansplaining)
- **Deception** → Subset of CHA (Corporate Speak, Gaslighting)
- **Performance** → Subset of CHA (Virtue Signaling, Trolling)
- **Intimidation** → Can be STR or CHA (Gatekeeping)
- **Investigation** → Subset of INT (Thrifting, Doxxing)
- **Insight** → Subset of WIS (Vibe Checking)
- **Medicine** → Subset of WIS (Crystal Healing, Self-Diagnosis)

