## CONTENT CREATION CHECKLIST

When creating ANY game content, verify:

- [ ] All bonuses reference one of the 6 core stats
- [ ] Damage specifies type AND associated stat modifier
- [ ] Skills map to exactly one ability
- [ ] Equipment bonuses are reasonable for rarity (+1 common, +2 uncommon, +3 rare, +4 very rare, +5 legendary)
- [ ] Class features specify which stat they key off
- [ ] Conditions have clear triggers and recovery methods
- [ ] Attack actions specify: target (CR), roll (d20 + stat + prof), damage (dice + stat mod + type)
- [ ] Defensive abilities specify: trigger, duration, stat (if any)
- [ ] Humor is maintained but mechanics are clear

